    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >帮助圣诞老人找回走失的驯鹿，为即将到来的圣诞节做好万全准备！在这场找物冒险中，可爱的圣诞鸭「叮当」会一步步引导你完成任务。你需要在细节丰富且精致的 3D 场景中，收集大量的圣诞小物和装饰品，并找出隐藏的圣诞点心。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030650/extras/3deeecab0cf6708451857c5e6f8b1607.poster.avif?t=1763985544\" width=616 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030650/extras/3deeecab0cf6708451857c5e6f8b1607.webm?t=1763985544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030650/extras/3deeecab0cf6708451857c5e6f8b1607.mp4?t=1763985544\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用隐藏的钥匙或拉杆解开门锁，试着打开所有看得见的箱子和容器，你便有机会发现关卡中的小彩蛋。温馨的主题音乐，配上丰富的圣诞场景，让你完全沉浸在欢乐的节日氛围之中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030650/extras/b22900a611b4686a4739bdc00e1496be.poster.avif?t=1763985544\" width=616 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030650/extras/b22900a611b4686a4739bdc00e1496be.webm?t=1763985544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030650/extras/b22900a611b4686a4739bdc00e1496be.mp4?t=1763985544\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以探索圣诞老人的家，也可以搭上特快列车直达节日博物馆！每个关卡都有各式各样的物品等着你去发掘，从不同国家的圣诞点心，到充满恶趣味的丑毛衣和特别的圣诞装饰，应有尽有。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >想要解锁全成就？你可以找出所有隐藏的点心与姜饼，或是清除所有陈年灰尘与蛛网，来挑战更高分数！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >快来体验一场奇妙的圣诞寻宝之旅吧！佳节愉快！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030650/extras/4960d270cdfe1543f0a4de9122c5bd44.poster.avif?t=1763985544\" width=616 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030650/extras/4960d270cdfe1543f0a4de9122c5bd44.webm?t=1763985544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030650/extras/4960d270cdfe1543f0a4de9122c5bd44.mp4?t=1763985544\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>游戏特色：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◾ 精致的全 3D 立体场景。只需轻点鼠标即可操作，无需键盘！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◾ 超过 100 种可供收集的独特圣诞小物和装饰品。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◾ 挑战找出 1000 多个隐藏点心，并清除所有灰尘、蛛网和杂物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◾ 尽情探索，享受轻松愉悦的圣诞假日氛围。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◾ 可用姜饼换取谜题提示。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◾ 查看物品，了解有趣的圣诞小故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◾ 内容丰富、风格温馨的圣诞音乐歌单。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
